cdata.name: BitStation
cdata.desc:
BitStation is a cryptocurrency trading and analysis system. It provides tools such as the Intelliscript and an automated trading feature in order to make it easier for the Bitstation user to make a trade decision. In addition, the platform makes possible for the users to require a trading advice by offering a certain amount to another user who is able to perform that task.

BSTN is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) token developed by BitStation and it is used as a medium of exchange within the platform. Furthermore, the users can pay membership fees and other users trading advice, as well as rewards, by using BSTN.
